    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在找一款轻松惬意的游戏吗？<br>那你来错地方了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throwing Knight 是一款具有完全非传统操作方式的高难度平台游戏。你会很快学会操作，但想真正掌握它，可是要付出心理代价的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/78522f2ba7cd4010f6ee71bd8f5b12fa.poster.avif?t=1765213086\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/78522f2ba7cd4010f6ee71bd8f5b12fa.webm?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/78522f2ba7cd4010f6ee71bd8f5b12fa.mp4?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在四个关卡中测试你的耐心，每个关卡都有独特的障碍和氛围。使用鼠标控制每一次跳跃的方向和力度。抓住链条荡过去，乘着小矿车前进，并躲开所有只为一个目的而设计的陷阱——让你死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/06145f1020004b610c8902b68cff160d.poster.avif?t=1765213086\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/06145f1020004b610c8902b68cff160d.webm?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/06145f1020004b610c8902b68cff160d.mp4?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到达检查点后，收集药水以获得至关重要的额外生命。记录你的通关时间和死亡次数，然后在下一次尝试中努力让数字下降。好好享受……也别太生气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/9b70ac0af9ea37bb4b4dbe8fadae581d.poster.avif?t=1765213086\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/9b70ac0af9ea37bb4b4dbe8fadae581d.webm?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/9b70ac0af9ea37bb4b4dbe8fadae581d.mp4?t=1765213086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得自己有实力吗？那就证明一下——马上把它加入愿望单！</p>",
